OVERVIEW
========

This is Msql::RDBMS, version 0.91, an HTML-based Relational Database
Management System for the Mini SQL database.

REQUIRED COMPONENTS
===================

Mini SQL 2.x (see http:://www.Hughes.com.au/)

Perl Modules (see your nearest CPAN mirror)

    CGI-modules-2.75.tar.gz
    Msql-modules-0.91
    Date::Format
    Date::Parse

A Web server

INSTALLATION
============

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

DOCUMENTATION
=============

Setting up a database schema:

  man sqldef.pl
or
  perldoc sqldef.pl

Using the module:

  man Msql::RDBMS
or
  perldoc Msql::RDBMS

THE FUTURE
==========

Keep an eye on:

http://www.ids.net/~bjepson

for late-breaking information and on-line demos (soon).

Have fun,

The Authors
(Brian Jepson <bjepson@ids.net>, Paul Sharpe <paul@miraclefish.com>)

